## Installation Guide

**Caution!** it can only be used along w/ `rpm` package management. `deb` has no such mechanism it depends to be functional.

#### Layouts

* scripts: the scripts used by myself to maintain devel:languages:nodejs on build service.
                    and test nodejs-packaging at runtime.
* nodejs: ruby modules needed by nodejs.prov and nodejs.req.
* tool: useful tools to package nodejs modules on openSUSE.

For a working package, packagers can see the specfile here: [nodejs-packaging](https://build.opensuse.org/package/show/devel:languages:nodejs/nodejs-packaging)
